            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hortaris in vitam <lb n="2"/>miscens adversa s&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>cu</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>dis <lb n="4"/>Clodius Hermogena <lb n="5"/>proconsulatu salu<lb break="no" n="6"/>bri <lb n="7"/>Theodoti cura lega<lb break="no" n="8"/>ti dedicat arcem <lb n="9"/>hos ego Ianuarius <lb n="10"/>versus formare cu<lb break="no" n="11"/>ravi 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftträger mit früherer Inschrift (AE 1902, 49b) für die Zweitverwendung um 180 Grad gedreht.</p>
            </div>
